{"tid":1566361,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（冷氣軍師召集）齊來向奶共美國議員施加壓力","createTime":"2019-09-13T14:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T08:15:01.000Z","uid":34891,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6543c8174219ca3f4f136825612f21ceb3506545","tid":1566361,"uid":34891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:10:15.000Z","msg":"要確保《香港民主及人權法案》高票通過，最後障礙係有奶共傾向嘅議員。今日睇到單新聞，竟然有民主黨議員反對通過法案<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（Source: <a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/junshiwaijiao/hj-09112019133536.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fjunshiwaijiao%2Fhj-09112019133536.html&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=deb65cc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/junshiwaijiao/hj-09112019133536.html</a>)<br />\n<br />\n我地要義正辭嚴咁同佢地講，香港民主及人權法案係必需要通過。冷氣軍師們，請大家踴躍去twitter 留言勸佢地支持法案（link: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/usip/status/1171786710063157249?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fusip%2Fstatus%2F1171786710063157249%3Fs%3D21&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=99dc8814\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fusip%2Fstatus%2F1171786710063157249%3Fs%3D21&h=64e49f77\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/usip/status/1171786710063157249?s=21</a>) 。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請記住，雖然同佢地道不同，但因為我地有求於人，所以明知佢地奶共都好，語氣要客氣d，我地目的係炸爆佢地twitter，營造民意壓力比佢地</span></strong>，等佢唔敢咁公然奶共。"},{"pid":"5dc8b93fbeba34e256fcc1d7145e7dfab88e2bca","tid":1566361,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:10:49.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthrHTWT.jpg&h=21d791c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87bd566f57befdc9d22e79a47a2b5243b04a0949","tid":1566361,"uid":34891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:11:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477f3983b97b0255482d3c7313cfaa99069ddf55","tid":1566361,"uid":34891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ec33611c057a71961e8ff0f778f9faeb4881bf","tid":1566361,"uid":34891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80fc927a95b92d54cf58e2d414571b2124933e9","tid":1566361,"uid":34891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ffcd86b5b0254940f13f34c2b728ab28c17363e","tid":1566361,"uid":306816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:17:17.000Z","msg":"[突發 - 國際線] Humans of New York 黎香港!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566182</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n求幫推啊! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾全世界睇到前線的真實經歷啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4284cb01735e89fddb07dd4cc545b364783ecb3f","tid":1566361,"uid":34891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece35a6c126585f4095bb94826dc02a7042e631a","tid":1566361,"uid":306816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor